Package: FEASTime
Type: Package
Title: Extending FEAST for Microbial Source Tracking in Time-Series Samples
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Ma", "Yanyan", email = "ma15091227920@163.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Extends the FEAST EM algorithm to longitudinal time-series data using
    a Markov chain-based iterative framework. Supports rarefaction, biologically-informed
    unknown source initialisation, and optional continuous source exposure modelling.
